971
01:03:13.525 --> 01:03:16.025
{\an8}Dia semakin dekat! Pandang sana!

972
01:03:16.037 --> 01:03:16.829
Apa itu?

973
01:03:16.913 --> 01:03:18.373
Berhenti!

974
01:03:18.873 --> 01:03:20.375
Saya beri amaran!
Jangan datang dekat!

975
01:03:20.458 --> 01:03:22.001
Saya tak mahu menembak!
Saya...

976
