1109
01:13:08.796 --> 01:13:11.257
Baiklah. hebat. Terima kasih.

1110
01:13:12.716 --> 01:13:14.468
Terima kasih banyak.
Saya...

1111
01:13:15.511 --> 01:13:16.887
Kita akan berjumpa nanti. okey?

1112
01:13:17.805 --> 01:13:19.598
